OL,3,CSaleswoman 'laughed at' after asking
OL,4,Cfor her old job back after becoming a
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FAn award-winning saleswoman who said
OL,8,Fshe was laughed at by her boss when
OL,9,Fshe asked to return to her role after
OL,10,Fgiving birth has won a maternity
OL,11,Fdiscrimination case.
OL,13,FSarah Lindup, 27, said that before she
OL,14,Ftook maternity leave she was "very
OL,15,Fsuccessful" in Bright HR Limited's web
OL,16,Fteam sales department, the tribunal in
OL,17,FManchester heard.
