OL,7,FMs Lindup gave birth to her daughter
OL,8,Fand went on maternity leave in
OL,9,FFebruary 2022, but after a new sales
OL,10,Fboss was hired she lost her former
OL,11,Frole, the tribunal was told.
OL,13,FShe attended the firm's awards
OL,14,Fceremony in May 2022 and was given two
OL,15,Fawards for being a both a "notably
OL,16,Fhigh-performing sales operative" and a
OL,17,F"highly-regarded team member".
