OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FThis included a "Millionaire Award" as
OL,8,Fshe had made #1.3 million for the
OL,9,Fcompany in a year, without working the
OL,10,Ffull 12 months, the tribunal heard.
OL,12,FJayde Stott became the new head of
OL,13,Fsales and the pair had a meeting in
OL,14,FOctober 2022 where they discussed Ms
OL,15,FLindup's return to work the following
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,18,FMs Lindup said that when she mentioned
OL,19,Freturning to the same team, Ms Stott
OL,20,Ftold her this would not be happening.
