OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FThe claimant added: "She laughed as
OL,8,Fthough my returning to the web team
OL,9,Fwas a ludicrous idea."
OL,11,FThe tribunal heard her income dropped
OL,12,Ffrom around #65,000 to around #24,000
OL,13,Fafter returning which had "disastrous
OL,14,Fpersonal consequences".
OL,16,FEmployment Judge Abigail Holt said it
OL,17,Fwas "striking" that the manager
OL,18,Frepeatedly referred to the meeting as
OL,19,Fa "mum-to-mum chat" despite it being a
OL,20,Fformal meeting.
