OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,F"It was irrational for the respondent
OL,8,Fnot to redeploy their award-winning
OL,9,Fweb team member, who only months
OL,10,Fearlier they had feted, back to the
OL,11,Fposition where she had a track record
OL,12,Fof bringing in #1.3 million in sales
OL,13,Ffor them in less than a year," she
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FThe judge said Ms Lindup's complaint
OL,17,Fof maternity discrimination was well-
OL,18,Ffounded and a remedy hearing has been
OL,19,Fscheduled for a later date.
